## Contributing

Before opening a PR:
1. If your change is non-trivial, write a spec in `specs/features/<area>/<slug>.spec.md`
2. Update tests as per Selective TDD (see CLAUDE.md)
3. Run linter and tests locally
4. Verify CI passes before requesting review

